      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Twisted Desire",
        "Client": "Smith\u0027s Son",
        "Description": "Those horns are so cool! Fit\r\nfor a name like \u0022Diablos\u0022 for\r\nsure, with that twisted shape.\r\nI\u0027d love to get my hands on\r\none and craft my store sign\r\nfrom it. I bet it\u0027d do wonders\r\nfor business!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Diablos",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "D\u00E9sir tordu",
        "Client": "Fils du forgeron",
        "Description": "J\u0027adore ces cornes !\r\nElles vont bien aux Diablos,\r\navec leur forme tordue.\r\nJ\u0027aimerais en r\u00E9cup\u00E9rer pour\r\nl\u0027enseigne de ma boutique.\r\n\u00C7a attirerait du monde !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Diablos",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Desiderio contorto",
        "Client": "Figlio del fabbro",
        "Description": "Che corna favolose! Con quella\r\nforma contorta, si addicono a\r\nun mostro chiamato \u0022Diablos\u0022.\r\nVorrei averne uno per creare\r\nl\u0027insegna del mio negozio.\r\nGli affari migliorerebbero\r\ndi sicuro!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Diablos",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Auf den Dreh gekommen",
        "Client": "Sohn des Schmieds",
        "Description": "Diese gedrehten H\u00F6rner sind\r\nso cool! Und dann auch noch\r\nder Name: \u0022Diablos\u0022. Ich h\u00E4tte\r\nzu gern eines von diesen\r\nDingern f\u00FCr mein Ladenschild.\r\nIch wette, die Kunden w\u00FCrden\r\nmir die T\u00FCr einrennen!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Diablos.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Deseo retorcido",
        "Client": "Hijo de herrero",
        "Description": "\u00A1Esos cuernos molan un mont\u00F3n!\r\nEl nombre de \u0022Diablos\u0022 le pega\r\nmucho teniendo esa forma\r\nretorcida. Me encantar\u00EDa hacer\r\nel letrero de mi tienda a\r\npartir de uno. \u00A1Seguro que es\r\nbueno para el negocio!",
        "Target": "Caza un Diablos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
